  <section id="safety-guidelines" class="section section-hidden">
   <div class="container">
    <h1 style="text-align: center; color: var(--primary); margin-bottom: 1rem; font-size: 2.5rem;">Safety Guidelines</h1>
    <p style="text-align: center; color: var(--subtle); margin-bottom: 3rem; font-size: 1.1rem;">Your safety and security are our top priorities</p>
    <div class="grid grid-2">
     <div class="card">
      <h3 class="card-title">üõ°Ô∏è For Service Providers</h3>
      <ul style="color: var(--text); line-height: 2; margin-top: 1rem;">
       <li>‚úì Verify customer identity before providing service</li>
       <li>‚úì Meet customers in safe, public locations when possible</li>
       <li>‚úì Share your service schedule with family members</li>
       <li>‚úì Use secure payment methods through our platform</li>
       <li>‚úì Report suspicious behavior immediately</li>
       <li>‚úì Keep communication on platform for safety</li>
       <li>‚úì Trust your instincts - decline uncomfortable requests</li>
      </ul>
     </div>
     <div class="card">
      <h3 class="card-title">üîí For Customers</h3>
      <ul style="color: var(--text); line-height: 2; margin-top: 1rem;">
       <li>‚úì Check provider ratings and reviews before booking</li>
       <li>‚úì Communicate service details clearly upfront</li>
       <li>‚úì Use secure payment methods on our platform</li>
       <li>‚úì Be respectful of provider's time and boundaries</li>
       <li>‚úì Report any issues or concerns immediately</li>
       <li>‚úì Verify service provider credentials when needed</li>
       <li>‚úì Keep interactions professional and courteous</li>
      </ul>
     </div>
     <div class="card">
      <h3 class="card-title">üí≥ Payment Safety</h3>
      <ul style="color: var(--text); line-height: 2; margin-top: 1rem;">
       <li>‚úì Always use platform's secure payment system</li>
       <li>‚úì Never share bank details or OTPs with anyone</li>
       <li>‚úì Get service confirmation before making payment</li>
       <li>‚úì Report payment disputes within 48 hours</li>
       <li>‚úì Keep transaction records for reference</li>
       <li>‚úì Beware of requests for advance full payment</li>
      </ul>
     </div>
     <div class="card">
      <h3 class="card-title">üì± Privacy Protection</h3>
