       <li>‚úì Control what information you share publicly</li>
       <li>‚úì Use platform messaging for communication</li>
       <li>‚úì Don't share personal documents unnecessarily</li>
       <li>‚úì Review privacy settings regularly</li>
       <li>‚úì Report spam or harassment immediately</li>
       <li>‚úì Be cautious about sharing home address initially</li>
      </ul>
